The accompany drawings, which are included to provide a further understanding of the invention and are incorporated in and constitute a part of this specification, illustrate embodiments of the invention and together with the description serve to explain the principles of the invention. In the drawings:
FIG. 1 illustrates a structure of a plasma display panel according to the present invention;
FIG. 2 illustrates detailed relationship of a scan electrode, a sustain electrode, and a barrier rib in a plasma display panel according to the present invention;
FIG. 3 illustrates a sectional structure of a plasma display panel according to the present invention;
FIGS. 4A and 4B illustrate reason why an overlap area of a sustain electrode and a barrier rib is greater than an overlap area of a scan electrode and a barrier rib; and
FIG. 5 illustrates a plasma display panel in which a channel is provided at a barrier rib.
